\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The PC Training is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education provider and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC.\line \line The Higher Certificate in Entrepreurship programme was tabled during the Accreditation Committee Meeting of 05 and 06 October 2011 and was not accredited for the following reason\'3A\line \line 1. A number of inconsistencies were noted in the submission\'3A the modules do not correlate with the modules as per the application form\'3B the credit values do not add to 120 credits\'2C but 130 credits\'3B the modules\'2C purposes\'2C credits\'2C outcomes and syllabus is that of the Diploma in Commerce\'2C and not for this programme\'3B the programme is at NQF level 5\'2C but the exit level outcomes are at level 6. \cell \pard 

